  "title": "General Manager",
  "description": "<p>Company Overview  </p><p>We are a Singapore-based food &\nbeverage (F&B) company engaged in restaurant operations, brand development,\nand market expansion.</p><p>Job Title: General Manager (Operations\n& Management)  </p><p>Employment Type: Full-time  </p><p>Location: Singapore  </p><p>Monthly Salary Range: SGD 12,000 – SGD\n15,000  </p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p>- Oversee day-to-day operations and overall\nmanagement of the company’s F&B business \n</p><p>- Ensure smooth operations across outlets,\nincluding service standards, staffing, and workflow management  </p><p>- Implement operational strategies to\nimprove efficiency, productivity, and profitability  </p><p>- Ensure compliance with Singapore food\nsafety, hygiene, and licensing regulations \n</p><p>- Manage budgeting, cost control, and\nfinancial performance  </p><p>- Supervise outlet managers and department\nheads  </p><p>- Coordinate with suppliers, landlords, and\nbusiness partners  </p><p>- Support business growth and new outlet\nsetup from an operational perspective  </p><p>Requirements:</p><p>- Degree in Business, Hospitality, or\nrelated field  </p><p>- At least 10 years of management\nexperience, preferably in F&B or hospitality operations  </p><p>- Strong experience in multi-outlet\noperations management  </p><p>- Solid understanding of cost control and\noperational efficiency  </p><p>- Leadership and team management experience</p>",
